hopobject.body: I enjoy travelling be natural organics sunscreen And there you have it. The Jaguars have traded Eugene Monroe. You think the Browns are the only that can play the “Punt” game? Nope. I wrote an article a few months back titled 3 Bold Predictions, and in that article I predicted this would happen. I don’t mean to toot my own horn, but, HONK HONK. I’m only being cocky because I think one of the negative comments was “we aren’t trading Monroe that would be beyond stupid”! Well we’re beyond it. I can see stupid in the rear view.
